com.tectonica.jonix.basic

Class BasicCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.basic.BasicCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class BasicCollection
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains the essential information included in ONIX2 <Series> / ONIX3 <Collection>

    NOTE: to access the information, read the (public final) fields directly. No getters() are included..

    May be constructed from either a Series or a Collection.

    Zach Melamed
